{"tid":558292,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《2018最強發明》一鍵上西天！安樂死名醫推「3D自殺膠囊艙」","createTime":"2018-02-12T06:53:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-05T13:01:22.000Z","uid":160807,"like":26,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"c55447199826796459275fe9fc739f9fcadf40a6","tid":558292,"uid":160807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T06:53:21.000Z","msg":"近幾年，大眾對於「安樂死」議題的想法逐漸開放，不少人主張，「安樂死走得更有尊嚴。」「每個人有權利決定自己的生死。」而今年，將有一台「3D自殺膠囊」誕生！<br />\n<br />\n澳洲有位長年推動安樂死的名醫，他叫做Philip Nitschke，又被稱為「死亡博士」。先前他對外表示，將在2018年推出一款名為「Sarco」的自殺膠囊艙。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://image.cache.storm.mg/styles/smg-800x533-fp/s3/media/image/2017/12/04/20171204-011824_U10834_M354788_dc1c.jpg?itok=CaHNt-wI\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimage.cache.storm.mg%2Fstyles%2Fsmg-800x533-fp%2Fs3%2Fmedia%2Fimage%2F2017%2F12%2F04%2F20171204-011824_U10834_M354788_dc1c.jpg%3Fitok%3DCaHNt-wI&h=1b7ad85d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nSarco具有流線外型，充滿科技感，艙體傾斜空間可容納一人。考量到環保議題，Sarco上方的膠囊艙部分，可於使用者斷氣後，直接拆下來當作棺材使用；而底座的部分，可以重複使用。<br />\n<br />\n想執行自己執行安樂死的人，必須先通過一個線上心理測驗，才會拿到一組「開艙密碼」。接著民眾可以至雲端下載Sarco藍圖，再以3D列印的方式，印出膠囊艙使用。使用者躺進艙內後要按下「死亡鍵」，艙內就會開始釋放液態氮、降低氧氣濃度，使用者最後會安詳地死去&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3024/3024885.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3024%2F3024885.jpg&h=0d1cc623&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nPhilip初步估計，列印一台Sarco的費用大約是1200元美金（約台幣36000元）。Philip認為，Sarco能讓使用者不靠任何藥物安樂死。Philip表示：「每個理性的成年人都有選擇平靜死亡的權利。」他也自豪地認為，這將是2018最強的發明！<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3024/3024883.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3024%2F3024883.jpg&h=cb73cfa4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2018最強發明！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f17c04051848ffb77ba6223c65d0ab2df4a2f880","tid":558292,"uid":65449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T06:56:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"883ca6e62c18f64c1067162196d4cd21f28c1ee4","tid":558292,"uid":33481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T06:59:11.000Z","msg":"好似唔錯"},{"pid":"ba4e92ecc02fe2d19fcb60c760710e1dfb9f25ce","tid":558292,"uid":12517,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T07:00:16.000Z","msg":"香港人既英雄<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7fc6ae768f60a51584b00941682d9633be72add","tid":558292,"uid":53498,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T07:01:48.000Z","msg":"死都要成皮嘢,跳樓好過"},{"pid":"59d04d74a11ad36302c15c799474211178a63f2f","tid":558292,"uid":108467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T07:02:42.000Z","msg":"艙內就會開始釋放液態氮、降低氧氣濃度，使用者最後會安詳地死去<br />\n<br />\n凍死咋？"},{"pid":"4c4e227b2fbacaf573cc0b044d58943d540ae083","tid":558292,"uid":23021,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T07:04:03.000Z","msg":"平d得唔得呀"},{"pid":"1e290e72b9609e373d9974656fa35c86f316203d","tid":558292,"uid":33481,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"59d04d74a11ad36302c15c799474211178a63f2f","tid":558292,"uid":108467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T07:02:42.000Z","msg":"艙內就會開始釋放液態氮、降低氧氣濃度，使用者最後會安詳地死去<br />\n<br />\n凍死咋？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T07:04:24.000Z","msg":"你iq...........唉"},{"pid":"705dc6762f529cce4d22eb1a8ca069c98a64e144","tid":558292,"uid":160807,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T07:09:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47a97292c3818a624a74a68185ddcde75cd92d62